spid
====

A Spider Solitair game for the command line.

You like playing Spider Solitair?
You love the command line?
You want to combine the two?

If you have answered yes to all three questions, this program is for you. Also, you are probably me.
To start playing, just start the program with  ruby spid.rb . Then, at the command prompt type  h<Enter> to access the online help.
